sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant LLS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Inline as Ragas Inline Provider<br/>(in-process)
    participant InfAPI as Inference API<br/>(in-process)
    participant DSIO as DatasetIO API<br/>(in-process)
    participant Remote as Ragas Remote Provider<br/>(in-process)
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KFPPod1 as KFP Pod: retrieve_data<br/>(ephemeral)
    participant KFPPod2 as KFP Pod: run_ragas<br/>(ephemeral)
    participant S3 as S3 Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        Note over Client,DSIO: Flow 1: Inline Evaluation
        Client->>LLS: POST /alpha/eval/run-eval<br/>(inline mode)
        LLS->>Inline: Dispatch to inline::trustyai_ragas
        Inline->>DSIO: get_rows_paginated()<br/>(in-process)
        DSIO-->>Inline: Dataset rows
        Inline->>InfAPI: LLM completions via LlamaStackInlineLLM<br/>(in-process, max_workers=1)
        InfAPI-->>Inline: LLM responses
        Inline->>InfAPI: Embeddings via LlamaStackInlineEmbeddings<br/>(in-process)
        InfAPI-->>Inline: Embedding vectors
        Note over Inline: Ragas evaluate() via asyncio.to_thread()
        Inline-->>LLS: EvalResult (scores + metrics)
        LLS-->>Client: JSON Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 235, 220)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Remote Evaluation (Kubeflow Pipelines)
        Client->>LLS: POST /alpha/eval/run-eval<br/>(remote mode)
        LLS->>Remote: Dispatch to remote::trustyai_ragas

        Remote->>K8s: Read ConfigMap trustyai-service-operator-config<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (kubeconfig)
        K8s-->>Remote: ragas-provider-image value

        Remote->>KFP: create_run_from_pipeline_func()<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OpenShift OAuth)
        KFP-->>Remote: Run ID
        Remote-->>LLS: Job ID (KFP Run ID)
        LLS-->>Client: Job submitted

        Note over KFPPod1,KFPPod2: Pipeline executes asynchronously

        KFPPod1->>LLS: GET datasets/rows<br/>HTTP/8321
        LLS-->>KFPPod1: Dataset rows (JSON)

        KFPPod2->>LLS: LLM inference + embeddings<br/>HTTP/8321
        LLS-->>KFPPod2: Inference responses
        Note over KFPPod2: Ragas evaluate()
        KFPPod2->>S3: Write results.jsonl<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials

        Client->>LLS: GET /alpha/eval/job-status (polling)
        LLS->>Remote: Check job status
        Remote->>KFP: get_run(run_id)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        KFP-->>Remote: Run status
        Remote-->>LLS: Status response
        LLS-->>Client: Job status

        Client->>LLS: GET /alpha/eval/job-result
        LLS->>Remote: Get job result
        Remote->>S3: Read results.jsonl<br/>Auth: AWS IAM (via s3fs/pandas)
        S3-->>Remote: Evaluation results
        Remote-->>LLS: EvalResult
        LLS-->>Client: JSON Response (scores + metrics)
    end
